---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
</head>
<body class="w-full max-w-screen-md mx-auto my-4 dark:bg-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300">
  <Header />
  <main class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class="px-4 md:px-16 flex flex-col md:my-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl w-full font-bold md:block">Chislon Chow</h1>
      
      <h2 class="text-sm md:text-base w-full font-semibold">
        Registered Psychotherapist
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="px-6 md:px-24 flex flex-col gap-4 my-4">
      <p class="w-full text-center text-base md:text-lg">
        My psychotherapy approach centers on : compassion, attachment theory, and being trauma-informed. I have helped individuals, couples, and families who speak English and Cantonese. Coming to Canada from Hong Kong, I have insight into both cultures. The psychotherapeutic modalities I may use include Emotionally Focused Therapy and Dialectical Behavioural Therapy. 
      </p>
    </div>    
    <div class="px-4 md:px-12 flex flex-col gap-4 mb-4 mt-32">
      <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg w-full font-semibold text-center">
        ðŸš¨Greater Toronto Area Mental Health Crisis Information
      </h3>
      <p class="w-full text-sm md:text-base">In case of emergency, you might want to call your emergency hotline 911. As needed, please consider reaching out to local 24-hour Crisis Hotlines, such as: </p>
      <ul class="text-sm">
        <li>
          <a href="https://988.ca/">Suicide Crisis Helpline</a>: 988
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.dcogt.com/408-helpline/">Distress Centre of Toronto Helpline</a>: 416-408-4357
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://yssn.ca/310-cope/">York Support Services Network Crisis Line</a>: 1-855-310-2673
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://kidshelpphone.ca/urgent-help">Kids Help Phone Helpline</a>: 1-800-668-6868
        </li>
      </ul>
      
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</body>
</html>
